body_html:
You have to git amend your commit to use the email you signed the CLA with.

https://patch-diff.githubusercontent.com/raw/tensorflow/tensorflow/pull/11760.patch shows that it is using the default github one, so you'll have to update it. Either send a new PR for it or git commit --amend and then force push!
